big one, the
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:the statistically predicted forthcoming NZ earthquake of great magnitude
Origin: [none]
Register: informal
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: probably borrowed from California but now deep in the NZ psyche
